Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.72,0:00:02.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.85,0:00:05.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nirvana was fired toward Caitshelter,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:10.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but thanks to the magic bombs \Nfrom Christina, it barely missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.57,0:00:14.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Tri-mens, Lyon, and Sherry \Nmanaged to make Christina fly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.16,0:00:16.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,with what little magic power they had left,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:18.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but Christina is crashing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.56,0:01:54.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nirvana has been sealed since long, long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.45,0:01:58.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is an ultra-inversion magic \Nwhich replaces darkness and light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.88,0:02:02.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The seal was broken deep \Ninside the Worth Woodsea
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:07.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,by the Dark Guild, Oracion Seis, who \Nwished to gain Nirvana for themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:12.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to prevent that, an alliance \Nof official guilds was formed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:17.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From Fairy Tail: Natsu, Lucy, Gray, and Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:22.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From Blue Pegasus: Hibiki, \NRen, Eve, and Ichiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From Lamia Scale: Lyon, Sherry, and Jura.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.03,0:02:30.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And from Caitshelter, \NWendy also participated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.70,0:02:37.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus Jellal, who should have sunk into the sea together with the Tower of Heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.04,0:02:38.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,also joined the fray.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:43.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After many fierce battles, Oracion \NSeis was finally defeated,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.37,0:02:49.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but with the appearance of Master Zero, Natsu \Nand the others are facing their greatest crisis!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:51.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:52.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.55,0:02:53.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to three!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:02:55.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just hope Zero's not there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:57.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will head to four.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.00,0:03:01.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My parfum tells me that it \Nis the closest one to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:03.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The map is what told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:06.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it really necessary to correct me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.80,0:03:08.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take five.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:09.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're six.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:14.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Power of Feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:33.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, this tunnel is long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.95,0:03:41.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, I'm here... Lacrima number two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.65,0:03:45.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So I gotta destroy this thing, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.85,0:03:55.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't look like Master Zero's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:04:01.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means someone else has to fight him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.44,0:04:06.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is lacrima number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:23.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:30.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... So, your memories have returned?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:35.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:42.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:48.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:50.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:58.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire ain't gonna work on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:05:01.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:05.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Natsu... Our only hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:06.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:07.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:14.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fire Dragon Slayer. Your magic power \Nincreases from the power of flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:19.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Power of flames?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:24.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You... Doesn't seem like your memories \Nhave totally returned at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.71,0:05:28.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as I said... I remembered \NNatsu, that is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.75,0:05:30.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will stop Nirvana.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.02,0:05:35.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What I am trying to do has not changed, Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:38.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:42.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not have any memories prior \Nto waking up in this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:46.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I was the worst kind of human trash...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:48.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not aware of it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.65,0:05:52.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All I know is it seems I caused \Nyou and Erza some great injury...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:56.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, I wish to protect Wendy's guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.34,0:05:57.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish to stop Nirvana.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:06:00.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish to be of help to all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:03.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:06.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sayin' you forgot all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.04,0:06:08.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get away with \Npretending to be my ally!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.79,0:06:12.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Natsu... Accept this flame!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.34,0:06:16.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I didn't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.65,0:06:18.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forget Erza's tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.99,0:06:21.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You... You...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:24.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You made Erza cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:31.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh... If you're going to squabble \Namongst yourselves, can you please do it elsewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:34.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:06:59.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:07.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to do me in, \Nyou can do it anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:10.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already on my last legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.35,0:07:14.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... The power to defeat that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:21.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Golden flames...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.70,0:07:27.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is the passage to the third lacrima.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.58,0:07:31.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should rest a little, Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:34.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I won't make it then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.27,0:07:38.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But... You can barely walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:40.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:44.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? \NI can walk just fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:51.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But... Even if I'm not so okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.35,0:07:54.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go saying that now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:58.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Men, men, men...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:08:02.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The passage to the fourth lacrima...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.11,0:08:05.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I must hurry, no matter what \Nhappens to this body of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:09.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Ichiya, of Blue Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.60,0:08:14.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will fulfill my duty to the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:17.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The fifth lacrima.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:19.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Zero is not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.46,0:08:23.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, he's at lacrima number \None, which Natsu headed towards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:26.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:35.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the flame of guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:41.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The passage to the sixth lacrima...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.41,0:08:48.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Carla...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.60,0:08:51.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Jellal is okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:54.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about others, \Nworry about yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:56.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you really do this, Wendy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:09:00.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! This is something I have to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.60,0:09:10.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal, do you feel okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:14.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can use Healing Magic, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:19.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you recover Natsu's magic \Npower during his fight with Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:21.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:27.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this crazy talk? Do you have any idea how \Nmany times she's used Healing Magic today already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.94,0:09:30.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Any more is impossible! You \Nknow that she's actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:30.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:36.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I will handle Natsu's recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:44.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember the unfathomable power \Nhe has... The power of hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:51.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You go destroy the sixth lacrima in my stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.22,0:09:53.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.85,0:09:56.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:10:02.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Slayer magic was designed to be an \Noverwhelming offensive magic for battling dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:05.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Air...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.22,0:10:07.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.47,0:10:09.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat the heavens themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:12.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of a dragon sleeps within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:16.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The heavens?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:34.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of a dragon... is within me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.54,0:10:37.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is to protect my guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:40.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Grandine! Lend me the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:44.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:51.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The flame of guilt?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:54.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need you to forgive me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:57.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want you to receive this power...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.11,0:11:01.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:09.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in the man... \Nthat Erza believes in...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:46.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:54.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:59.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I've gotten your power, Jellal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.47,0:12:04.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The flame of guilt?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.56,0:12:09.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By eating that, you take on the same sin...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.55,0:12:11.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.67,0:12:14.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For a Fairy Tail wizard,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.51,0:12:17.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the true sin is averting one's eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:23.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and no longer being able \Nto believe in anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.21,0:12:48.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This power...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:52.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That light...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.99,0:12:59.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:06.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This lacrima isn't just \Nbig, it's also damn hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:10.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can sense a ton of magic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.81,0:13:12.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The lacrima is near.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:16.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This parfum reeks of danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.53,0:13:19.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am close. Men.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:22.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is near.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:26.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:30.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy, concentrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.92,0:13:33.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:12.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This power is similar to \Nwhen I ate Etherion...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.90,0:14:20.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa... It's like my power's \Ndoubled, or even tripled...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.39,0:14:29.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:32.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The final form of Dragon Slayer Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:39.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Its magic power is said to rival that of a \Ndragon's, capable of annihilating anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:42.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Annihilation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.21,0:14:44.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:48.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, I can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.93,0:14:51.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me with the power of a dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:54.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:06.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it... The third lacrima...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:09.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, hang in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:13.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it wasn't the time to show off,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.06,0:15:16.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but I wasn't able to say I couldn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.70,0:15:19.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:22.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm completely out of magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:28.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I want to protect Wendy's guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:30.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to get down on myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:35.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm going to keep \Ngoing, until the bitter end!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.94,0:15:40.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.13,0:15:43.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't fall! Not in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:48.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:50.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.45,0:15:53.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For Caitshelter...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.10,0:15:57.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For Jellal, who believed in me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:16:01.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And for all my other friends, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:10.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Gravity!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:21.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now... You can do better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:30.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.88,0:16:37.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:52.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.56,0:17:19.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Delete!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.90,0:17:50.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I can't pass out yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:54.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hibiki, Ren, Eve...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:57.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:23.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,3 more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.66,0:18:29.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:38.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all there is to \Nthe power of a dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:43.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragons ruled in ancient times \Nwith this paltry amount of power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.97,0:18:51.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you going to do, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:53.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:57.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but maybe if \NI throw myself against it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:18:59.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to destroy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:05.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give up! I won't \Ngive, up no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.05,0:19:09.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, it's that feeling \Nthat can give you the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:15.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We were listening back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:17.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We heard your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:19.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gemini...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.35,0:19:22.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.23,0:19:30.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can copy your body and abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.72,0:19:33.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll become your will!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.24,0:19:40.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We just need to destroy this thing \Nin about three minutes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:41.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.03,0:19:44.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Men... Men...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.13,0:19:48.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will show you my power parfum!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:05.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,More power... The power of the heavens...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.95,0:20:12.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the master of Oracion Seis, Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.36,0:20:16.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on a whole other level than a \Nmere foot soldier from some guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:26.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way trash like \Nyou could handle me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.03,0:20:33.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:36.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear them...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.82,0:20:42.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can... hear them...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.82,0:20:47.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear everyone's voices... I \Ncan sense everyone's feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.86,0:20:51.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not alone... Everyone's feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:58.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They support me... They are what \Ngive me the will to stand and fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.23,0:21:11.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess it's about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.02,0:21:15.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.99,0:21:17.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Gate of the Golden Bull is good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.68,0:21:19.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:26.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is the time to show everyone the \Ntrue power of Ichiya, of Blue Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.58,0:21:27.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Requip!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.09,0:21:38.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Power... Power is welling \Nup from within me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.70,0:21:39.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.94,0:21:48.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The power... The power of my \Nfriends flows throughout my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.36,0:21:54.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Force... It will be a shame \Nto crush it to smithereens, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.00,0:21:56.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.06,0:21:58.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:02.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will give you true nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.40,0:22:05.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My greatest magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.57,0:22:07.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Secret Dragon Slayer Art:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.92,0:22:10.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blazing Explosive Flame Edge!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.31,0:22:11.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Genesis Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.33,0:22:17.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Vanish into the great nothingness!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.90,0:23:59.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if there's a dragon walking around \Nsomewhere, that's just fallen through the cracks...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.79,0:24:02.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a dragon would fall through a crack!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.00,0:24:06.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had a dragon, I'd be able to train with \Nmy Dragon Slayer Magic whenever I wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.27,0:24:11.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu! What do you want with \Na dragon when you have me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.26,0:24:13.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you look like you \Njust said something cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.20,0:24:16.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: I'm with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.76,0:24:18.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, there's no way you could do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.49,0:24:22.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I feel like it, I can go \Ntoe-to-toe with any dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.79,0:24:24.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,More like, toe-to-head.
